  "title": "High-resolution profiling of bacterial and fungal communities using pangenome-informed taxon-specific long-read amplicons - PubMed",
  "description": "Pangenome-informed microbiome profiling enables the tracking of microbial community dynamics in complex environments and overcomes limitations in phylogenetic resolution. Video Abstract.",
